          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Plutonium source, 12.7 g of PuO2, encapsulated in",
                " brass cylinders, 0.64 mm thick, to stop alpha and beta",
                " particles. The encapsulated source surrounded with a",
                " 0.5-mm silver foil to stop low energy gamma rays of",
                " 241Am.",
                "Isotopic composition of source: 89.56 % 242Pu,",
                " 0.74% 238Pu, 1.33% 239Pu, 6.37% 240Pu and 1.62% 241Pu,",
                "  and 0.42% 241Am, produced from beta decay of 241Pu.",
                "The source was placed in center of Gammasphere."
              ]
            },
